 /***************************************************************************************************************/    
                      // Test Step 4
                     // Check all cores are in running state except Core0
                    // stub Code to Check ISR Counter incrementing except Core0
                   // Check all CPU States shall be running state = FALSE, except Core[0] = TRUE
                      
  /***************************************************************************************************************/
  //Check All tasks of Core0 are stopped
